steps.name: Given  **I am on the XE currency converter page**
When  **I convert "10" "GBP – British Pound" to "EUR – Euro"**
Then  **I should see the result of "10" "Euros"**
assert expected **1 GBP = 1.13654 EUR** to include **GBP**
assert expected **1 GBP = 1.13654 EUR** to include **EUR**
And  **I should see the unit values for both "GBP – British Pound" and "EUR – Euro" in the conversion result.**
